<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mtqyd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- mtqyd bqywd mn nạr mtslsl mḥạwṭny ạlʿạr
 ḥyạty ạ̉kạdẖyb wkẖdạʿ wạlqlb mlyạn mrạr
 1-(bḍḥk wạlḥzn mlyny myt wmyn yḥyny
 bṣrkẖ yạrb tnjyny mn mwly̱ ʿzyz jbạr)2
 bḥbk ạ̉kyd bḥbk ḥạss ḥqyqy ạ̹ny ạ̹bnk
 nfsy ạ̉trmy̱ fy ḥḍnk wtdyny rwḥ ạlạ̹ntṣạr
 2-(ḍʿfy hw ạlly qạtlny mḥtạj yạyswʿ tlmsny
 kẖạṭy wdmk ygẖslny wlyl yṭlʿlh nhạr)2
 (kẖạṭy ạ̉nạ kẖạṭy wạ̉tẖm w hạ̉kẖd qrạr ḥạsm
 lạzm ạ̉twb ạ̉nạ lạzm kfạyh dẖl wạ̹nksạr)2</lyrics>
